Dialogue: 0,0:00:-06.-31,0:00:-02.-73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-02.-71,0:00:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world for you who seek freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.13,0:00:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stretches out right before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.30,0:00:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your endless dreams are your guide,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.30,0:00:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,surpass them, under the flag of your beliefs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.48,0:00:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.98,0:00:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.49,0:00:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.66,0:00:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.00,0:00:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the summer sun\Nsways the sails of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.11,0:00:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the cue to open the door to a new world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.62,0:01:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailing through the rocky waves of despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.62,0:01:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We head beyond the horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.30,0:01:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.97,0:01:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.65,0:01:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.99,0:01:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a trap! A trap by the navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.61,0:01:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sail on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.94,0:02:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! A pirate ship,\Ncoming out of the mountains?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.62,0:02:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Whereabouts of the Island Treasure!\NAttack of the Zenny Pirates!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.98,0:02:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.65,0:02:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't act so reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.32,0:02:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His heart hasn't stopped, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.32,0:02:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, cut that out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.66,0:02:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old-timer! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm finally out at sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.60,0:03:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really have become a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! This is no longer my coffin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.61,0:03:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the good pirate ship Zenny!\NIsn't that right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.95,0:03:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We told you, don't egg him on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.62,0:03:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a sick man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.29,0:03:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to pull,\NZenny the Moneylender?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your profession is to extort\Nmoney from pirates, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave up lending money long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'm Zenny the Pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you sell the navy short, you old geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.97,0:03:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man, watch yourself!\NHe's after your treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.31,0:03:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Lately, the navy has taken to\Ngoing after treasure on the side,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.98,0:03:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in addition to capturing pirates, have they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite industrious of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.25,0:03:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nami, bring the ship over.\N--Got it. Come on, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.59,0:03:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you! Don't give Nami-san any orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.59,0:03:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant Minchy!\NThe Straw Hats are on the move!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contact Captain Moore's fleet for backup!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:04:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.60,0:04:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I'd give you your cut of the treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.61,0:04:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand, don't you?\NWe can't let the captain know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way I figure it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're keeping your men hushed\Nup to take on this side project.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.62,0:04:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must cost a pretty penny,\Nhuh, Mr. Sergeant?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you dotty old coot!\NDon't think you won't pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some nerve,\Ntrying to swipe my treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.97,0:04:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come and take it from me, if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.98,0:04:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show them how a pirate fights!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.94,0:05:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--There!\N--You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.61,0:05:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a pirate, then you won't mind\Nit when the navy kills you, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.95,0:05:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, does the old\Nman have any sort of weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me what you've got! Take on\Nmy class 10-ranked abacus skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His abacus and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.63,0:05:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the goats.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.97,0:05:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys, idiots?\NWhat are you shooting at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:06:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't waste your\Nbullets like that! I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! They're goats!\NYou're taking on goats!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because they're goats\Nthat I can't do it, Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! The battle has already begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop watching the goings-on from\Non high, and come on down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We know. Stand aside for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Relax, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old-timer is in no physical shape\Nto be doing anything so crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.24,0:07:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Shoot them!\N--Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you've done it!\NMy boys are out of control!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.92,0:07:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look! They're waiting for us in formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.27,0:07:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange how they don't show\Nany signs of movement, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.27,0:07:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to think up a battle\Nplan now, while we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.94,0:07:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what shall we do?\NBe the first ones to attack them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.61,0:07:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't be crazy!\N--In any case...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.28,0:07:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we have to\Nhelp the old-timer! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.95,0:07:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, did we hit something a minute ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh? Did we?\N--Never mind! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.89,0:07:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Moore, there's no response\Nfrom Sergeant Minchy's ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that sound of\Ngunfire we heard earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.90,0:07:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we advance?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.23,0:07:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not yet. Wait for Minchy to report in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.57,0:08:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you guys go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough out of you, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.25,0:08:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.59,0:08:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.61,0:08:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's all that energy you had a moment ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.61,0:08:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zenny the Pirate, are you out of breath?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.95,0:08:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you've finally come forward,\Nyou little miscreant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are a talkative bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.23,0:09:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, shall we get down to business?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.90,0:09:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is your treasure located,\NZenny the Pirate?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.59,0:09:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, Corporal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you report this sooner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.59,0:09:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry, Captain Moore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.27,0:09:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a sneaky stunt to pull!\NThat miserable Minchy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.27,0:09:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that was what he was up to!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you spit it out, already?\NYou don't want to die yet, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do value my own life. I cherish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:10:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you, I'm penniless.\NWhat do you want me to spit out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.29,0:10:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even manage any spittle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.63,0:10:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As dinky an island as this is,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.64,0:10:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it won't take much work to dig\Nit up from one end to the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.98,0:10:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no further need of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.32,0:10:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're through!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I seem to have broken your abacus.\NSorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.27,0:10:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can defy the\Nnavy and get away with it--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.28,0:10:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old-timer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:11:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are late! I almost died, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.95,0:11:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Waah! I was so worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.96,0:11:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoke Star!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.29,0:11:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's far enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.63,0:11:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin, this is where you were?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man, you can relax,\Nnow that Captain Usopp is here--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened? That bump is huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no pulse!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.31,0:11:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Chopper. I'm over here, over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.31,0:11:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that! Here, take it easy, and lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you die, old-timer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.32,0:11:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I would die?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.66,0:11:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel fine, of course. I'm finally a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:12:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel like dying anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.28,0:12:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just came to the island\Non the sergeant's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.96,0:12:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... well, I guess subordinates\Ncan't go against their superiors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, our captain is pretty\Ncapricious himself, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.97,0:12:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't go getting too chummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Old man, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, lad?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief, there's just no helping Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.31,0:12:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your seizure has passed, so that's a relief, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Much obliged, Dr. Chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that. Old man, how's tricks?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.59,0:12:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just fine, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, right. Listen, Gramps,\Nyou can tell us now, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:12:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About your treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't go giving any shocks to my patients!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.94,0:13:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old-timer, stay strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.94,0:13:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the love of...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess you have done a lot for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so maybe I can tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's more like it! Look,\Nthe navy knows about it, and all,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.62,0:13:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it must be an amazing treasure, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,0:13:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did... have a treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pirates who owed me signed over\Na whole heap of treasure to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.63,0:13:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, thinking of buying a pirate ship,\Nand getting my pals together,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.64,0:13:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I exchanged all of it for cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.97,0:13:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cash!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking back on it, that's when my fate turned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you last night that I was\Nattacked by those who had owed
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,money to me, and I ended up\Ndrifting ashore on this island, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, naturally, I managed\Nto protect the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.26,0:14:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I'd risked my life for that\Nmoney in order to buy my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I came to, after\Nwashing up on the beach...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It was eaten?!\N--Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.62,0:14:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of it?! They ate all of it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.95,0:14:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Well, maybe\Nthey left two or three bills.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.63,0:14:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, like I told you,\Nthese guys are my treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.30,0:14:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of my fortune may have been lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.64,0:14:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but in return, I gained my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.97,0:14:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't betray me, or try to cheat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.64,0:14:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I have friends at my side,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.58,0:14:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who don't do anything for selfish motives.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, I want to reward them for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.25,0:14:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've obtained the greatest\Ntreasure in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.59,0:14:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.59,0:15:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it is good. I'm a man that\Ntakes advantage of every situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.60,0:15:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a load of crap! Hey, Straw Hat!\NThis fight isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.27,0:15:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a pristine fleet over\Nthere just waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.61,0:15:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think you're going to get away so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.94,0:15:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go trying to act cool\Nwhen you're rolling around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.28,0:15:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he, stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.95,0:15:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the stupid ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.28,0:15:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can stand up\Nto a fleet of nine ships?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.96,0:15:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell them that if they want a fight,\Nto come straight at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.63,0:15:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy! A little bit higher!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.64,0:15:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.57,0:15:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Pistol!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.58,0:16:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, direction is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... disgrace to the navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.26,0:16:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Take him away!\N--Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.27,0:16:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Naval Captain Moore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no interest in the island,\Nor in this man Zenny.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.28,0:16:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My only goal is to bring you down,\Nin the name of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.62,0:16:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To show my gratitude for turning over\Nthis misguided member of my fleet,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.29,0:16:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will allow you to choose where we fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.29,0:16:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, bring your ship out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were thinking of leaving pretty soon, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be coming toward you right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, old man, I fixed it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I should have known. Much obliged.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.58,0:17:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.25,0:17:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is all set up through\Nsupper. You just have to cook it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, much obliged.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, lads, are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're facing a fleet of nine ships, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not just strong, I'm lucky, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't keep up with you, lad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old-timer, I made up a whole supply for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so make sure you take your medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.94,0:17:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, all right, all right. I'll make\Nsure I take it, don't you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's been fun, Gramps!\N--Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, you take care of the old-timer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see you later, out on the seas somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Once I finish repairs to the ship,\NI'm going to be setting sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:18:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be waiting for you, Zenny Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.58,0:18:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's head back to\Nthe island for a bit, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.91,0:18:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to fix the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, everyone off. We're going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.90,0:19:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Age doesn't have anything to do\Nwith becoming a pirate, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.57,0:19:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My word, he knows how to get\Nan idea in someone's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.91,0:19:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper is a patient one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.91,0:19:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many years will I need to\Ntake this whole stack of medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.58,0:19:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Much obliged, everyone. Very much obliged.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.59,0:19:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, I think I can\Ntough it out a little while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.26,0:19:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, my life as a pirate has just begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice going, inviting them into\Nthe foggy reef area, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.28,0:19:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, you do use your head, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.28,0:19:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.95,0:19:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I do"...? That's what I was asking you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.62,0:19:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Moore's Fleet, calling any\Nships sailing in this area of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Moore's Fleet!\NRequest immediate assistance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you are such a moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I hadn't complimented you! I take it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.97,0:20:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.63,0:20:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like he was thinking about that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pure chance. He was just\Npointing his finger wherever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.98,0:20:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, ship's doctor, how is it, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.32,0:20:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps' condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.32,0:20:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That medicine controls his episodes, at best.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't keep him from getting any worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.66,0:20:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His heart was fairly weak to\Nbegin with, and as old as he is,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.33,0:20:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sailing on a ship, let alone as a pirate...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.00,0:20:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.27,0:20:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old man said he wanted to\Nbe a pirate, so we should let him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.61,0:20:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, once the old man sets out to sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.94,0:20:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he may find an island that\Nhas a cure for his illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.62,0:20:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.28,0:21:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have to worry about it too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.62,0:21:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That old man isn't going to croak that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.62,0:21:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His weak heart notwithstanding,\Nhe did have plenty of guts, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.63,0:21:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right, Chopper. We'll see him again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.64,0:21:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hmm, sure we will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.31,0:21:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be waiting for you, Zenny Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.49,0:21:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, beyond the never-ending sky
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future that I once saw\Nis now starting to take shape
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.95,0:22:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are days where I almost lose to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.46,0:22:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happened, there was\Nsomeplace warm I could go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.83,0:22:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The friends I took pride in\Nalways, without fail,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.97,0:22:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,pushed me onwards, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.99,0:22:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the stars are pouring\Ndown underneath the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.26,0:22:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This unique moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.60,0:22:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An island! I see a lighthouse, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.60,0:22:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then they've got something to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.60,0:23:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's incredibly tall, huh?\NIs that really a lighthouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.61,0:23:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind about that, let's hurry\Nand get something to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Who are you, Pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.61,0:23:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, not another weird old man!\NI'm not taking care of this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.95,0:23:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.28,0:23:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Legend of the Rainbow Mist!\NOld Man Henzo of Luluka Island"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.29,0:23:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
